high_descs: Turn around, move across the room, turn right from the stove, and face the counter with a potato
Pick up the potato from the counter
Take the potato and go to the microwave
Open the microwave, place the potato by the side of the egg on the microwave plate, warm it for a few seconds, take the potato out, and close the microwave
Turn around and turn back to face the microwave
Place the potato on the cabinet top with the microwave by side of the fork
anns.task_desc: Place a heated potato on the cabinet top

high_descs: Turn around, hang a right at the stove and walk to the counter.
Pick up the potato in the middle of the counter.
Turn right and walk to the black table with the microwave on the right.
Put the potato inside the microwave, heat it, remove it and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the microwave table on the right.
Put the heated potato near the edge of the table to the left of the fork.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated potato on a table.

high_descs: Turn around, go forward to the stove top, turn right, go forward to the counter.
Take the potato from the counter.
Turn right, go forward, turn left to the microwave next to the fridge, go to the microwave on the dresser.
Cook the potato in in the microwave, take the potato from the microwave.
Take a step to the left, face the microwave.
Put the potato to the left of the fork on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked potato on a dresser.
